Package: honolulu.gov
Title: Honolulu Open Data (Socrata) API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the City and County of Honolulu open data
    portal (data.honolulu.gov). Traffic incidents, HPD crime incidents, 311 service
    requests, building permits, budget data, business registrations, and generic
    SODA API access to all 70+ datasets.
